===Women's One-Day International captains===

This is a list of cricketers who have [[captain (cricket)|captained]] the [[New Zealand women's cricket team]] for at least one [[women's one-day international]]. The table of results is complete to the end of the Women's World Cup in 2004/5. The next ODI has not yet been scheduled. New Zealand's greatest ODI success was under [[Emily Drumm]] when they won the 2000/1 World Cup.

